{"tid":462642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【大嬸變女神】46歲鍾麗緹扮性感女僕 突擊上酒店搵「嫩夫」","createTime":"2017-11-08T17:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T04:11:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ac315e64c1062ebc7ab5e75cc0403ac145eed0","tid":462642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171108/small/1510154308_ec43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171108%2Fsmall%2F1510154308_ec43.jpg&h=510c45ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n46歲鍾麗緹，去年今日同細佢12年嘅大陸藝人張倫碩結婚，婚後不時在網上晒恩愛，無奈天下間嘅花生友對女性似乎都係比較「要求高」，左一句「大嬸」又一句「肥」，真係好現實。<br />\n<br />\n之前有報道話影到張倫碩同鍾麗緹現身機場，張倫碩全程只顧玩手機，於是網民又揣測兩人感情生變，又有人調侃鍾麗緹「女神變大嬸」，話佢「快要把褲子撐破」，激到張倫碩要喺微博貼文反擊：「別老是拿我老婆體重說事！」又大讚鍾麗緹係全世界最正嘅女人：「這就是你，一個我尊重和愛的女人」，仲話：「你現在我喜歡。你以後我也喜歡！」<br />\n有個咁錫自己嘅老公，鍾麗緹當然識做&mdash;&mdash;俾身在長沙開工嘅老公一個驚喜&mdash;&mdash;化身性感女僕，敲老公度房門。<br />\n條片嘅credit係「碩帝國影像出品」，條片一開首就係「啱啱瞓醒」嘅鍾麗緹，一臉慵懶，用嗲到爆嘅聲線「嬌喘」了一下，伸個懶腰同大家say hi「大家好」，然後話今日係結婚一周年啦，之後鏡頭一pan，咦，老公不在床上，於是鍾麗緹話要俾個驚喜佢。<br />\n鏡頭一轉，就見到鍾麗緹去做gym啦，又揀戰衣啦&mdash;&mdash;就係呢件性感女僕裝。整個過程鍾麗緹表情萌到爆，又yeah又yes又飛吻，就連介紹送俾老公嗰盒蛋糕，都要「揸住把聲」，令人忍唔住要搵衫著。<br />\n咁當然鍾麗緹唔係著住件女僕裝就咁上飛機。去到老公下榻嘅酒店，確認目標，然後鏡頭一轉，已變身嘅鍾麗緹以手機鏡頭當鏡，又嘟嘴又傻笑極誇，然後敲門扮house keeping。<br />\n好老實，鏡頭落咗effect，加埋佢個濃妝，真係唔講都唔知佢係鍾麗緹。<br />\n然後就係張倫碩開門個呆樣。<br />\n鍾麗緹張開雙手嗌：Surprise！你需要毛巾嗎？<br />\n如果你係張倫碩，你會點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171108/57435246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57435246&d=gXDHcVhkjiWzOhIxOqKrko9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=01158ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57435246&h=627d9c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171108/57435246</a>"},{"pid":"e89fd18ac712806e8311fcfa869ffee2728f74ae","tid":462642,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171108/large/1510154308_ec43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171108%2Flarge%2F1510154308_ec43.jpg&h=f2fdf8f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef8dbb2a737fee2d2d5dcf841ced0f1b0dbb269a","tid":462642,"uid":72638,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248f2d8e2e4ca7f40dca357e02e5f8fa8e396e7e","tid":462642,"uid":8511,"like":111,"dislike":6,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿麗好正喎！<br />\n當年我見柔道部同空手道大師兄都好鍾意佢"},{"pid":"2d29a378a288d0620fd98095c8c77a744ddf95dd","tid":462642,"uid":29014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿麗好正喎！<br />\n當年我見柔道部同空手道大師兄都好鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"